author: Fextralife
description:
Hell is Us Gameplay Preview - The Most INTERESTING Game I've Played In YEARS!
In this video, I'm going to be talking about my hands-on impressions of Hell Is Us. This is a game that I got to play back in August at Gamescom. I have been under NDA for over a month. If you can remember back in our Phantom Blade Zero Gamescom coverage. I mentioned that there was a game that I really really enjoyed from the event that I couldn't talk about. This is the game I was referring to.

0:00 Hell Is Us Gameplay Impressions
0:26 What is Hell is Us
0:51 Combat and Gameplay
11:13 Combat Balancing and Future Changes

author: Fextralife
description:
Elden Ring Nightreign Recluse Guide - How to play Recluse in Nightreign
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, we're going to take a look at Recluse and how to play him in combat. We'll cover her stats, skills, recommended relics, weapons to look out for, and how to use her effectively in a party. So if you're playing Recluse or planning to learn this class, then this video is for you.
